WEBVTT

1
00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:05.766
My daughter blames me for being too cruel back then

2
00:00:05.766 --> 00:00:08.266
Kicked you and your mother out of the gun

3
00:00:08.300 --> 00:00:09.733
Is that all?

4
00:00:09.733 --> 00:00:12.233
Ah no I shouldn't

5
00:00:12.900 --> 00:00:14.166
Infidelity in marriage

6
00:00:14.166 --> 00:00:17.566
Jiang Hongda, my mother loves you so much, but you betray him

7
00:00:17.566 --> 00:00:19.800
I'll never forgive you for that

8
00:00:19.933 --> 00:00:21.966
The Jiang family went bankrupt and closed down irretrievably

9
00:00:21.966 --> 00:00:24.000
You also taste the taste of not having a home

10
00:00:24.100 --> 00:00:27.200
You made up your mind not to forgive me

11
00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:28.566
And made me kneel

12
00:00:28.566 --> 00:00:31.000
Can't I just tease you?

13
00:00:34.466 --> 00:00:38.466
Retribution, this is the retribution I deserve.

14
00:00:38.466 --> 00:00:41.200
What kind of garlic are you packing here?

15
00:00:41.766 --> 00:00:43.933
If it weren't for Mr. Gu

16
00:00:43.933 --> 00:00:45.866
What do you think you are?

17
00:00:47.400 --> 00:00:50.100
Then my boyfriend just became the richest man

18
00:00:50.100 --> 00:00:52.233
Piss you off

19
00:00:52.666 --> 00:00:56.066
It's all your fault if you hadn't seduced me back then

20
00:00:56.066 --> 00:00:59.400
How will our guns go bankrupt?

21
00:00:59.400 --> 00:01:01.100
I'll kill you.

22
00:01:04.400 --> 00:01:05.766
To fight out

23
00:01:05.766 --> 00:01:07.400
Don't dirty my office.

24
00:01:07.466 --> 00:01:08.900
Come with me!

25
00:01:13.933 --> 00:01:15.966
Thank you for helping me today.

26
00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:19.066
Now only Jiang Xue is left, and I will vent my anger for you.

27
